{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~pazzani/Slides/MLC94/tsld006.htm", "content": "\r\n<HTML>\r\n\r\n<HEAD>\r\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Context-Type\" CONTEXT=\"text/html;charset=windows-1252\">\r\n<meta name=\"GENERATOR\" content=\"Microsoft Internet Assistant for PowerPoint 97\">\r\n <TITLE>Decision Tree Test Selection Metrics</TITLE> \r\n</HEAD>\r\n\r\n<BODY     >\r\n\r\n <H1>Decision Tree Test Selection Metrics</H1> \r\n <P><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>I-GAIN (ID3)\r\n</H2>\r\n</UL><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>GINI (CART)\r\n</H2>\r\n</UL><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>GINI + Altered Priors (CART)\r\n</H2>\r\n<UL>\r\n<LI>Use altered probability that an example belongs to a class\r\n<BR>\r\n<BR>\r\n<BR>\r\n<BR>\r\n<BR>\r\n</UL></UL><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>Select test with minimum misclassification cost of partitions</H2>\r\n</UL></P>\r\n<P></P> \r\n<P>\r\n<TABLE>\r\n  <TD HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=100> <A HREF=\"tsld005.htm\">Previous slide</A> </TD>\r\n  <TD HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=100> <A HREF=\"tsld007.htm\">Next slide</A> </TD>\r\n  <TD HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=150> <A HREF=\"tsld001.htm\">Back to first slide</A> </TD>\r\n  <TD HEIGHT=100 WIDTH=150> <A HREF=\"sld006.htm\">View graphic version</A> </TD>\r\n</TABLE>\r\n<BR>\r\n</P>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</Body>\r\n</HTML>\r\n", "encoding": "ascii"}